{"tid":2299153,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請問ADMIN諗住幾時正視用FAKE NEWS帶風向嘅問題？","createTime":"2020-11-24T14:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T08:36:59.000Z","uid":308915,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2c14350b04cc2b7fff37205f2c3e6e6295ebe22a","tid":2299153,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"已經連續兩日有疑似三毛打手利用主流媒體曲解當事人意思嘅「新聞」走上嚟連登帶風向意圖誤導一眾會員<br />\n而且已經唔係第一次透過post fake news嚟屈人「認輸」<br />\n請問幾時先可以正視相關問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通下下都要靠正常巴絲喺事後出post澄清先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n[11月23號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[11月24號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[慎防左膠帶風向］鮑威爾代表美國人控告選舉舞弊，並非代表侵侵團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n左報話侵律師團輸左三十幾個case , Jenna Ellis  辟謠話係 Fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296773</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[持續慎防五毛左膠帶風向］美國聯邦總務署只提供選舉後財政資助，唔會確認邊個係下屆總統。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n《正視聽》GSA署長公開講明自己、家人、同事受到極大人身安全威脅，但依然拒絕承認拜登勝選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298222</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n密切根州聯邦上訴法院批准選舉審查 , 將於星期三上午9點舉行聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298731</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"046b99f65db39270f258b9336c24c1823108a971","tid":2299153,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a90e048544c6a13ca99dda31f8d1a69441b1026","tid":2299153,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"［慎防風向撚荼毒］美國大選真&middot;FACT-CHECK posts整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fbbb2fe810d912768ac2f3e71eb85f8406bfbb6","tid":2299153,"uid":100237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"連仔 入嚟望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac82f10e488a583b89f035554466baeca0ba0c0c","tid":2299153,"uid":15045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4dd55ed959df07e8a9c4aada96604916741cb4","tid":2299153,"uid":249979,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"連尼住選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得之前有幾個Po標題勁快被TAG左&quot;來源有待核實&quot;之類既野<br />\n而家呢d美媒fake news帶風向就唔TAG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5633c111e6c0c9fa2a8d7ec9d2e809e6823cfc22","tid":2299153,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:56:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e12ff056043dd1a512240a3a1c1068deb97f728","tid":2299153,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"全美都係咁<br />\n小小admin可以點做？"},{"pid":"610ace07b8d2a7e208569dd0b99b373f64ef7369","tid":2299153,"uid":308915,"like":2,"dislike"