>\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bb21994a2e3008f48c80433717acfa5aacc6a81","tid":2299153,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:22:22.000Z","msg":"Report極啲fake news 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bac586d1ddafb5e7311f196e2486ec3b6c9fc79","tid":2299153,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c14350b04cc2b7fff37205f2c3e6e6295ebe22a","tid":2299153,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"已經連續兩日有疑似三毛打手利用主流媒體曲解當事人意思嘅「新聞」走上嚟連登帶風向意圖誤導一眾會員<br />\n而且已經唔係第一次透過post fake news嚟屈人「認輸」<br />\n請問幾時先可以正視相關問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通下下都要靠正常巴絲喺事後出post澄清先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n[11月23號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[11月24號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[慎防左膠帶風向］鮑威爾代表美國人控告選舉舞弊，並非代表侵侵團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n左報話侵律師團輸左三十幾個case , Jenna Ellis  辟謠話係 Fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296773</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[持續慎防五毛左膠帶風向］美國聯邦總務署只提供選舉後財政資助，唔會確認邊個係下屆總統。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n《正視聽》GSA署長公開講明自己、家人、同事受到極大人身安全威脅，但依然拒絕承認拜登勝選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298222</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n密切根州聯邦上訴法院批准選舉審查 , 將於星期三上午9點舉行聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298731</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:27:52.000Z","msg":"點解啲人咁容易比人FAKE到？香港嘅教育水平都算高架喎"},{"pid":"cfb30a23ed5e118c1fa1c1b9bf968aa423b4fd9c","tid":2299153,"uid":116917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T23:31:18.000Z","msg":"連仔請正視下"},{"pid":"6cb728e58ba6056ea739b49af9e792f2f7147b4e","tid":2299153,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"Admin唔洗ban?<br />\n<br />\n突發！特朗普政府正式認輸！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76737e3424719c359d999a4527830ba1359a7056","tid":2299153,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"一句講曬！貼安心出行嘅黃店仲幫唔幫襯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一堆pr 有目的咁想整死黃店"},{"pid":"ae50fb055c14ba93282229e4b50fb324e075ed60","tid":2299153,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾連狗選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dllm"},{"pid":"2d46a8572b6dc96fdb90ce14936e6a771afc780e","tid":2299153,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"連狗會繼續扮死"},{"pid":"9e8a3fc1c57b06d1f22174da5f8e82ccef87cec3","tid":2299153,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},